dvl_skl.name: Extinction Ritual: Action
dvl_skl.desc:
Inflicts Dark damage (Magic, Power: 300) to a single enemy, then lowers the Dark Attribute Affinity of a single enemy by 2 levels.
The following effects will be added to this skill depending on the count of Malice on the skill holder:
1 Count of Malice: Adds the following Chain Effect, which activates when the attack is successful: Inflicts Dark damage (Magic, Power: 100) with a Bulwark-piercing effect on a single enemy.
2 Counts of Malice: Adds the following Chain Effect, which activates when the attack is successful: Decreases the DEF of all enemies by 20%. (1 turn)
3 Counts of Malice: Adds the following to the effect for 1 count of Malice: Causes the target to lose 2 MP.
4 Counts of Malice: Adds the following to the effect for 1 count of Malice: Applies 1 count of Spirit Chains of Indignation to the hit enemy.

dvl_skl.name: God's Domain: Action
dvl_skl.desc:
Adds Dark Pierce.
Damage received will decrease by 30% for each count of Malice on the skill holder.
Activates the following Chain Effect at the start of the 1st turn: Places 4 counts of Malice on the skill holder.
Activates the following Chain Effect at the end of the enemy turn: Decreases the Malice count of the skill holder by 1.
Activates the following Chain Effect when the skill holder downs a demon: Adds 1 count of Malice to the skill holder.
Activates the following Chain Effect at the end of own turn, or when the skill holder reaches 5 counts of Malice: Inflict 99,999  fixed damage on all enemies.
*Damage inflicted by this skill ignores all death prevention skills.
